Fansub!

21
00:05:46,110 --> 00:05:49,030
El camino del travesti.

22
00:05:55,790 --> 00:06:04,820
¡Oh, ven por mi camino!

23
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:29,590
¡Sí!

24
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:34,100
¡Sí!

25
00:06:34,100 --> 00:06:36,270
¡Un, deux!

26
00:09:13,190 --> 00:09:14,820
¿De verdad?

27
00:10:53,140 --> 00:10:55,790
Mola

28
00:10:53,140 --> 00:10:55,790
Shi

29
